   <topic>CURRENT_RECORD_NUMBER Function</topic>
   <syntax>Record_Number as N = current_record_number()</syntax>
   <description>Returns the current record number.</description>
   
   <example><![CDATA[
dim ptr as P
ptr = form.view("Customer Information")
ptr.Fetch_Last()
? current_record_number()
= 28
]]></example>
  
